title: Other Account Stuck In Transferring
body:
I finally got to OCE and was planning on switching my EUW account to OCE i went through many struggles to even get to the stage im currently at. Although i payed the rp and no longer can log into my EUW account from the region saying "Your account transfer is in progress, this should take a few minutes" and so far its been half an hour and cant log into the account on OCE or EUW. Please Help!

Account Name Wanting To Be Transferred - JohanneSkorte

Ive made multiple tickets and still havent been replied too for 3 days!

This is quite annoying )^:{{item:3348}}

replies.body: I do not even see a purchase option under account for me as I am trying to transfer out of Oceania.  Maybe service is down?
you cannot transfer out of OCE till middle november unless you transfer by ticket by October 10th. On the OCE boards there is a post with more detail

Looks like we did have a few issues with region transfers that dealt with OCE for a bit. I do see your ticket in the queue right now and an agent should be handling it shortly! Don't fret too much, those agents will be able to get your account transferred over for you!
